                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Displaying the hospitality that a xenia spirit was denied in life can avert its wrath. A plate of food, mug of fine drink, or similar fare held in one hand can be Raised as a Shield and used to Shield Block the spirit's attacks as if it were a buckler; a creature can Shield Block in this way even if they lack the feat.</p>"
                },
